Interface ContentTypeHandler

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractContentTypeHandler, FormUrlEncodedHandler, HtmlHandler, JacksonLibHandler, JacksonXmlHandler, JsonLibHandler, MultipartFormDataHandler, XStreamHandler

    public interface ContentTypeHandler
    Handles transferring content to and from objects for a specific content type
